Cerebral Blind	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.IllithidSlayerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:After reaching 6th level, an illithid slayer is protected from all devices, powers, and spells that reveal location. This ability protects against information gathering by clairsentience powers or effects that reveal location. The ability even foils bend reality, limited wish, miracle, reality revision, and wish when they are used to gain information about the slayer's location (however, metafaculty can pierce this protective barrier). In the case of remote viewing or scrying that scans an area an illithid slayer is in, the effect works, but the slayer simply isn't detected. Remote viewing or scrying attempts that are targeted specifi cally at an illithid slayer do not work. This ability is active as long as the slayer is psionically focused.	KEY:Illithid Slayer ~ Cerebral Blind																										SORTKEY:Class_Illithid_Slayer	SOURCEPAGE:EPH													
