Power Known	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.PsionUncarnateClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:At every level indicated on Table 6-6, a psion uncarnate gains additional power points per day and access to new powers as if he had also gained a level in whatever manifesting class he belonged to before he added the prestige class. He does not, however, gain any other benefit a character of that class would have gained (bonus feats, metapsionic or item creation feats, psicrystal special abilities, and so on). This essentially means that he adds the level of psion uncarnate to the level of whatever manifesting class the character has, then determines power points per day, powers known, and manifester level accordingly. If a character had more than one manifesting class before he became a psion uncarnate, he must decide to which class he adds the new level of psion uncarnate for the purpose of determining power points per day, powers known, and manifester level.	KEY:Psion Uncarnate ~ Power Known																										SORTKEY:Class_Psion_Uncarnate	SOURCEPAGE:EPH													
Incorporeal Touch	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:ClassFeatures.PsionUncarnateClassFeatures.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Beginning at 1st level, a psion uncarnate can make up to three melee touch attacks per day that each deal 1d6 points of damage if they hit. The character's Strength modifi er is not applied to this attack, but it is effective against incorporeal creatures (and against corporeal creatures while the psion uncarnate is incorporeal) The character's hand and arm seem to become slightly translucent when he makes these attacks. A miss still counts as a use of the ability. While uncarnate (see below), a psion uncarnate can make melee touch attacks at will that do not count against his uses of this ability. For every four levels higher than 1st the psion uncarnate attains, the damage on these attacks increases by 1d6 points.	KEY:Psion Uncarnate ~ Incorporeal Touch				DEFINE:IncorporeatTouchTimes|0					BONUS:VAR|IncorporealTouchTimes|3									ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Psion Uncarnate ~ Incorporeal Touch ~ 1|PREVARGTEQ:PsionUncarnateLVL,1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Psion Uncarnate ~ Incorporeal Touch ~ 2|PREVARGTEQ:PsionUncarnateLVL,5	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Psion Uncarnate ~ Incorporeal Touch ~ 3|PREVARGTEQ:PsionUncarnateLVL,9						SORTKEY:Class_Psion_Uncarnate	SOURCEPAGE:EPH													
